@node Main "BulGom - Documentation"

                              'BulGom' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'BulGom' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} in which you try to burst as many
coloured bubbles as possible. A bubble will burst if it is at its
maximum size, otherwise it will grow up in size. Also, as you click
on bubbles and no other bubble burst, new bubbles will appear
randomly on the game board.

  You get points when surrounding bubbles burst along the bubble you
clicked on. However you will make much more points if the bubbles
are all of the same colour.

  Have fun!

