@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place 'BulGom' where you want
on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or
Libraries are needed. The only requirement is that your Workbench must
have 8 colours or more.

                             How to play?

  At the start of the game, 8 bubbles of 4 different sizes and
colours are placed in the center of the game board. To play the
game, click on any bubble, if the bubble is at its maximum size,
it will then burst, otherwise it will increase in size.

  When a bubble burst and there are surrounding bubbles of the same
size, they will also burst and you will get one point for each burst
bubble, except the one you clicked on. If those bubbles are all of
the same colour, the scoring will be calculated according to the
following table:

    2 bubbles = 5 points
    3 bubbles = 20 points
    4 bubbles = 45 points
    5 bubbles = 80 points
    etc.

  One little complication though: as there are bubbles of 4 different
sizes; every time you click on a bubble and it either increase in
size or if it burst and no other bubble burst, a new bubble will
appear on the game board... beware that the game board does not fill
up completely because if that happens, the game will be over.

  The game keeps the best score made since the game was run.

  Have fun!

